com.vmware.vcenter.identity

Interface ProvidersTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Providers
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProvidersStub

    public interface ProvidersTypes
    The Providers interface provides methods to list, read and modify vCenter Server identity providers. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.0.

      static class  ProvidersTypes.ActiveDirectoryOverLdap

      The ConfigType class contains the possible types of vCenter Server identity providers.
